| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-5072 — Recovery Inhibition (werewolves)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 9e9f3cbb-fc09-59d1-b0a9-bc85d61db812"
